com.vmware.vcenter.trusted_infrastructure.trust_authority_clusters.kms

Interface Providers

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ProvidersTypes, Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProvidersStub

    public interface Providers
extends Service, ProvidersTypes
    The Providers interface provides methods to create, update and delete Key Providers that handoff to key servers. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.0.
